video.title: All Hail King Julien
video.synopsis: In this Emmy winner for Outstanding Children's Animated Program, Madagascar booty-shaker King Julien takes on the jungle’s craziest adventures.

episodes.synopsis: Uncle King Julien abdicates his throne, handing off his crown to Prince Julien. Let the reign of King Julien the Thirteenth begin!
episodes.title: King Me

episodes.synopsis: King Julien learns that 99% of the lemurs love him, so he makes it his mission to find and convert his one "hater."
episodes.title: Poll Position

episodes.synopsis: The evil genius Karl sets out to destroy King Julien. When both Clover and Maurice are captured, King Julien must save them from his new nemesis.
episodes.title: Enter the Fanaloka

episodes.synopsis: Exhausted from settling his subjects' disputes, King Julien replaces himself with a dummy king so he can play hooky, unwittingly sparking a rebellion.
episodes.title: Empty Is the Head

episodes.synopsis: Set on reclaiming his throne, Uncle King Julien convinces Julien to go into Foosa territory. Julien creates a disguise and forces Maurice to join him.
episodes.title: Return of the Uncle King

episodes.synopsis: Clover is forced to take a vacation, and while she's away, she meets the handsome and free-spirited Sage Moondancer.
episodes.title: Eat Prey Shove

episodes.synopsis: Julien teams up with Timo the tenrec, a scientist who the king enlists to automate everything in the kingdom.
episodes.title: He Blinded Me With Science

episodes.synopsis: When Julien embarrasses Maurice, he tries to make up for his transgression, while Mort inadvertently joins an anti-King Julien group.
episodes.title: Viva Mort

episodes.synopsis: Julien concocts an elaborate lie, blaming a giant "mega-gecko" for ruining a young lemur's birthday party.
episodes.title: The Really Really Big Lie

episodes.synopsis: Julien finds a bag of coffee beans in the Cove of Wonders and gets the entire lemur community hooked on caffeine.
episodes.title: One More Cup

episodes.synopsis: King Julien has a brilliant idea: He'll tame a Foosa and train it to keep peace in his kingdom. But the plan doesn't go quite as expected.
episodes.title: My Fair Foosa

episodes.synopsis: Julien sparks a fashion frenzy when he turns a box of diapers into the coolest styles the kingdom has ever seen.
episodes.title: Diapers Are The New Black

episodes.synopsis: It's love at first sight when Julien meets Clover's party-girl sister, Crimson. Could the king have found his queen?
episodes.title: Crimson and Clover

episodes.synopsis: When Julien is fooled into believing that a "divine pineapple" contains the wisdom of former kings, a jealous Mort tries to get rid of it.
episodes.title: Pineapple Of My Eye

episodes.synopsis: Fascinated by the idea of money, King Julien brings cash to the kingdom. But Mort's surprising money skills create big problems.
episodes.title: Gimme Gimme Gimme: The Game

episodes.synopsis: When King Julien's body double is injured on a waterslide, it's up to Magic Steve to hold peace talks with the cranky crocodiles.
episodes.title: Body Double

episodes.synopsis: Julien rescues a charming old lemur named Doc Sugarfoot from a cave and takes him on as an adviser.
episodes.title: Election

episodes.synopsis: Thinking Mort is his son, Julien renames him Falcon and enters him in the Junior Gent pageant. Little does he know the lemur's true age.
episodes.title: Daddy Julien

episodes.synopsis: Rob, Julien's former best friend and partner in the rap duo "Lemurs Love the Lemur Ladies," shows up to lure the king back to his wild partying ways.
episodes.title: That's Sooo Rob

episodes.synopsis: Julien gives up his kingdom to help a fellow royal in distress, only to discover he's been tricked by two old enemies.
episodes.title: The Man in The Iron Booty

episodes.synopsis: After setting out to claim the moon for all lemurkind, King Julien comes face-to-face with Stanislav, the Russian Space Monkey.
episodes.title: Monkey Planet

episodes.synopsis: When Julien discovers Maurice is moonlighting as an adviser to Rat King Joey, the best friends break up and ask the divine pineapple for advice.
episodes.title: True Bromance

episodes.synopsis: While writing Julien's life story, Clover makes up a tall tale about a baby-eating giant scorpion named Fred. The real Fred reads it and vows revenge.
episodes.title: The King Who Would Be King

episodes.synopsis: After Frank the Sky God demands that the lemurs sacrifice King Julien, Julien creates his own deity: Larry the Volcano God.
episodes.title: Are You There, Frank? It's Me, King Julien

episodes.synopsis: Julien's dream of opening a nightclub finally comes true, but the place is haunted by a masked phantom. Or could it be someone making mischief?
episodes.title: The Phantom of Club Moist

episodes.synopsis: Julien is diagnosed with Mad Horse Disease but refuses to give up the throne to his uncle without a fight … or maybe a steeplechase.
episodes.title: King Juli-END?

episodes.synopsis: Julien is missing and mangos are in short supply. Village life couldn't get any crazier . . . that is, until Julien's royally annoying parents arrive.
episodes.title: O Captain My Captain Pt.1

episodes.synopsis: Clover and Mort race to rescue their king as Julien tries to avoid the pirates' plank by showing off his prime "pirate recruit" booty moves.
episodes.title: O Captain My Captain Pt.2

episodes.synopsis: As his parents prepare to leave, Julien tries to reclaim his childhood by forcing them to attend the dance recital they missed when he was a kid.
episodes.title: Dance, Dance, Resolution

episodes.synopsis: When his parents grant his wish for a brother by adopting the socially toxic Brodney, Julien goes overboard making Brodney feel like a royal.
episodes.title: Oh Brother Where Aren't Thou?

episodes.synopsis: Julien panics when his parents announce they are never leaving. His plan to scare them off backfires when Karl takes the idea too far.
episodes.title: Love Gauntlet

episodes.synopsis: Julien bets that his team can beat Uncle King Julien's, and he puts the whole kingdom on the line. The only problem? Julien's star athlete is dead.
episodes.title: Jungle Games

episodes.synopsis: Aliens keep abducting Mort, making Julien jealous. Can Clover and the gang help the king get face time with the aliens before an invasion begins?
episodes.title: Close Encounters of the Mort Kind

episodes.synopsis: To boost the kingdom's patriotic spirit, Julien starts a fake war on butterflies. But lemur pride is tested when the insects counterattack for real.
episodes.title: The Butterfly War

episodes.synopsis: Eager to create fast food for the kingdom, Julien holds an idea contest. But will the winning entry be a dining delight or a cooking curse?
episodes.title: Fast Food Lemur Nation

episodes.synopsis: Julien is sure that his beloved jumping bean was stolen and becomes obsessed with security. To Clover's dismay, he arms the village with scorpions.
episodes.title: Get Off My Lawn

episodes.synopsis: Julien sees the Lemur School reunion as a way to relive his glory days, but his old flame Karen and his foe Karl have a dangerously different agenda.
episodes.title: Revenge of the Prom

episodes.synopsis: Clover must choose between royal duty and family pride after she's invited to compete in the Tournament of the Doomed and Julien forbids her to go.
episodes.title: Eye of the Clover

episodes.synopsis: When his peace treaty leads to unrest and a broken boom box, Julien wants to build a wall to keep non-lemurs out of the party kingdom.
episodes.title: Run for the Border

episodes.synopsis: Bored by Xixi's news reports, Julien unveils a new programming lineup that whips the whole kingdom into a frenzy.
episodes.title: The All Hail King Julien Show

episodes.synopsis: A bump on the head leaves Clover thinking she's a character from her adventure stories. The others must play along to save her from a terrible fate.
episodes.title: The Neverending Clover

episodes.synopsis: An incredible painting by Mort sets the whole kingdom abuzz, ruining Julien's plan to become the next big art star.
episodes.title: Who Arted?

episodes.synopsis: When Masikura warns the island is about to sink, Julien races to find a way off, while Maurice and Clover scour the kingdom for his lost baby toy.
episodes.title: That Sinking Feeling

episodes.synopsis: After ridding the kingdom of a noisy jungle rooster, King Julien is haunted by guilt and decides to mount a rescue mission.
episodes.title: The Jungle Rooster

episodes.synopsis: Inspired by an old-fashioned book of manners, King Julien sets out to host a debutante ball. But his new etiquette coach takes the training too far.
episodes.title: The Good Book

episodes.synopsis: With Julien sick and the others away on a cruise, Mort poses as king to entertain a judge from a big competition -- with disastrous results.
episodes.title: The King and Mrs. Mort

episodes.synopsis: Timo's magic touch turns King Julien's ragtag band into a pop music sensation. But not everyone is happy with the group's new sound.
episodes.title: King Julien Superstar!

episodes.synopsis: When King Julien pops a mysterious mixtape in the boom box, the weird sounds activate a secret agent brainwashed by his uncle.
episodes.title: The Panchurian Candidate

episodes.synopsis: A glitch in King Julien's new cloning machine unleashes a swarm of ravenous Morts led by a tiny tyrant -- and not even Timo knows how to stop them!
episodes.title: The Wrath of Morticus Khan

episodes.synopsis: During a wild nighttime adventure, King Julien befriends a lonely warrior named Koto, who stirs up strong feelings in the kingdom.
episodes.title: Koto, Plain and Tall

episodes.synopsis: A shocking discovery sends Maurice on a quest to find his true destiny. Meanwhile, Julien gets a taste of what his life would be like without Mo-Mo.
episodes.title: I, Maurice

episodes.synopsis: As the mountain lemurs close in, Julien challenges his former bro Koto to an epic dance-off for control of the kingdom.
episodes.title: Un-King Me

episodes.synopsis: King Julien announces he's turning over a new leaf and seeks anonymous suggestions from his subjects on how to improve their kingdom.
episodes.title: Julien 2.0

episodes.synopsis: Tired of being passed over for manly assignments, Ted brings back his macho alter ego, Snake. Julien uses Xixi's talk show to boost his image.
episodes.title: Spin Cycle

episodes.synopsis: An allergy to gecko milk transforms King Julien into a werewolf-like Night Creature, forcing Clover to fulfill her family legacy as a monster hunter.
episodes.title: Night Creatures

episodes.synopsis: A missing persons case turns Julien into a film noir gumshoe. But just when he thinks he's solved it, things get more mysterious.
episodes.title: Tears in the Drain

episodes.synopsis: When Julien's new adviser brings social media to the jungle, it has a disastrous effect on his entourage and nearly costs him the kingdom.
episodes.title: Squad Goals

episodes.synopsis: With Julien's help, Karl faces off against his older brother, who wants to replace all of Madagascar's tea stands with “Brüs by Bruce” coffee kiosks.
episodes.title: One More Cup, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After finding a barrel of plant food, Julien decides to supercharge his mango trees. Unfortunately, he ignores Timo's limit on how much food to use!
episodes.title: There Will Be Juice

episodes.synopsis: When Julien puts his kingdom's students in an islandwide academic tournament, their dismal performance spurs him to overhaul the lemur curriculum.
episodes.title: Blackboard Jungle

episodes.synopsis: Julien rigs an election to make Maurice feel more important, pitting him against Mort. But things get out of hand when “Political Mort” takes control.
episodes.title: Lord of the Fruit Flies

episodes.synopsis: After announcing that he and Chauncey will be retiring, Karl hosts a Willy Wonka-inspired competition to choose his replacement as Julien’s nemesis.
episodes.title: Karl-Mageddon

episodes.synopsis: Uncle King Julien makes one final attempt to take over the kingdom. But romance distracts him, causing him to lose sight of his own evil plan.
episodes.title: King Julien Is Watching You

episodes.synopsis: After Clover announces she'll soon be leaving the kingdom, Julien realizes he'll need an army for defense and appoints himself as a drill sergeant.
episodes.title: The End Is Near

episodes.synopsis: When Julien throws a bachelor party and accidentally loses the groom-to-be, he has Timo and Dr. S. build a Franken-groom to stand in at the wedding.
episodes.title: The End Is Here
